item.title: CVE-2023-31275|2023-11-27T18:00:07.348Z -- wps -- wps%20office
item.description: An uninitialized pointer use vulnerability exists in the functionality of WPS Office 11.2.0.11537 that handles Data elements in an Excel file. A specially crafted malformed file can lead to remote code execution. An attacker can provide a malicious file to trigger this vulnerability.
